quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  57,1,"Whatever is in the heavens and earth exalts Allāh,<sup foot_note=197495>1</sup> and He is the Exalted in Might, the Wise.",footnotes:197495:1
  57,2,"His is the dominion of the heavens and earth. He gives life and causes death, and He is over all things competent."
  57,3,"He is the First<sup foot_note=197499>1</sup> and the Last,<sup foot_note=197498>2</sup> the Ascendant<sup foot_note=197497>3</sup> and the Intimate,<sup foot_note=197496>4</sup> and He is, of all things, Knowing.",footnotes:197499:1,footnotes:197498:2,footnotes:197497:3,footnotes:197496:4